## Escalation Path

| Issue | Severity | Response Time | Owner | Escalate To |
|-------|----------|---------------|-------|-------------|
| Compilation error | High | Immediate | Dev | Tech Lead |
| Appium regression | High | Immediate | Dev + QA | Product Manager |
| Memory leak | High | 1 hour | Dev | Tech Lead |
| Decode failure | Medium | Next day | Dev | Tech Lead |
| Console warning | Low | End of phase | Dev | Tech Lead |

